PMAUTOAE is a CP/M archive utility that will dissolve standard LHARC (.lzh)
archives.  It also creates its own format archives, which aren't quite
standard LHARC archives, and thus won't be compatable with CS-DOS's lhx or the
Unix, Amiga, or MS-DOS lharc.

PMAUTOAE.COM is a self-dissolving archive.  Run it like any other CP/M
program, and it will dissolve itself into its constituent files.
